<p>Searching custom field values can be done with
<strong>.<em>CFieldName</em>:<em>keyword</em></strong>
e.g; <tt>.tags:spam</tt>.
Negation is also permitted by prepending a <tt>-</tt>
i.e; <tt>-.tags:spam</tt> finds ham.
Alternatively for tags, use the cloud of links below:</p>

<& /Elements/TagCloud &>
